@startuml

actor Pilgrim
participant Agent
participant Event
participant Package
participant Reservation
participant Hotel
participant Transport

' === Agent sets up the system ===
Agent -> Event : Create and manage events
Agent -> Package : Create and manage packages
Agent -> Hotel : Configure hotels
Agent -> Transport : Arrange transport
Agent -> Reservation : Oversee reservations

' === Pilgrim interaction ===
Pilgrim -> Agent : Contact agent for trip info
Agent -> Event : Show available events
Event -> Package : List packages for this event
Package -> Transport : Show transport details
Package -> Hotel : Show hotel options

Pilgrim -> Agent : Request to book package
Agent -> Package : Select package for pilgrim
Agent -> Reservation : Create reservation
Reservation -> Hotel : Assign hotel
Reservation -> Transport : Confirm transport
Reservation -> Event : Link to event

Pilgrim -> Agent : Make payment (total, paid, remaining)
Agent -> Reservation : Update payment status

@enduml
